/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/02/142603_8af0e5f88daced67f8ff4e8b2920a5bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F02%2F142603_8af0e5f88daced67f8ff4e8b2920a5bb.jpg&h=e7c4a3c1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n修羅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n56lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6733acf63ddfa485db4f28133b53be3d66847e6b","tid":183453,"uid":62421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:29:34.000Z","msg":"尹志平  唔見你申請  你再申"},{"pid":"952a99b88c47d3623b84a86b62fa83306f86f78c","tid":183453,"uid":16343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原來刷到4星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/02/142603_8af0e5f88daced67f8ff4e8b2920a5bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F02%2F142603_8af0e5f88daced67f8ff4e8b2920a5bb.jpg&h=e7c4a3c1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n修羅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f33700349af250119a25539ee4b7d046902f894","tid":183453,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:30:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Q&amp;A 睇左先好問</span></span></div></strong><br />\n1) 洗唔洗刷首抽 ?<br />\n刷首抽game <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2) 點刷 ?<br />\n綁定AC (Email)再登出 揀Guest入就可以再刷<br />\n普遍黎講係用晒佢送1400元寶 + 每日免費抽 + 3-6星抽獎卷 * 2<br />\n共7抽<br />\n<br />\n3) 點先可以開局 ?<br />\n首先要知咩係啱屬 : 背景 金 &gt; 銀 &gt; 銅<br />\n吳國 火屬<br />\n魏國 水屬<br />\n蜀國 木屬<br />\n他國 火屬<br />\n另外亦有武將 唔啱屬都會勁過其他啱屬 如各名將 王元姬 呂玲綺 <br />\n可參考 <a href=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201704/4fbc6b0eb1ef8178e1db254fd5c6f651.JPG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F201704%2F4fbc6b0eb1ef8178e1db254fd5c6f651.JPG&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=9cf03a09\" target=\"_blank\">https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/201704/4fbc6b0eb1ef8178e1db254fd5c6f651.JPG</a> <br />\n(僅作數值比較 參考下好 技能 攻速等亦需考慮)<br />\n<br />\n理想 : 5-6星 啱屬 不過刷100個帳都未必有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尚可/平民 : 4星啱屬 2-3隻 含可刷技能武將為佳<br />\n包括 周泰 太史慈 董卓等<br />\n可參考 <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1RoMaQMO8TOxb-luydTYzPSa91XKSkQ6y7LN0SDr0aJM/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1RoMaQMO8TOxb-luydTYzPSa91XKSkQ6y7LN0SDr0aJM%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=7219e6c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1RoMaQMO8TOxb-luydTYzPSa91XKSkQ6y7LN0SDr0aJM/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n<br />\n裝備亦都重要 有5星武器可考慮開局<br />\n<br />\n4) 打到第幾關先會儲到3000元寶10抽 ?<br />\n玩到你卡關都唔會有 一係等拎登入獎勵 一係課金 <br />\n<br />\n5) 卡關點算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1. 搵好友手動打 試多幾次<br />\n2. 刷關升LV 武將LV都好重要 另外仲刷埋裝 / 技能 (食自己可升技能)"},{"pid":"b7d992f7289e2dd202643ddebafe50d1cadf3758","tid":183453,"uid":39887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:30:23.000Z","msg":"屌我叫我老豆一齊玩啦 點知佢免費抽就中隻六星啱屬孫堅屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c1e261018304c07bf01a9ba0138e46676e3ab0","tid":183453,"uid":87546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T0