,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:31:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌我叫我老豆一齊玩啦 點知佢免費抽就中隻六星啱屬孫堅屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同老豆講6星最廢<br />\n3星最強 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}